   [bullet.jpg] Mike Fisher's Petition for Allowance of Appeal to the
   Pennsylvania Supreme Court in Commonwealth v. Steven Barry Scher:
   Attorney General Mike Fisher today asked the Pennsylvania Supreme Court
   to hear his appeal of a Pennsylvania Superior Courts opinion that
   reversed Dr. Stephen Schers first-degree murder conviction for the
   killing of his friend Martin Dillon.

